@startuml m1_node_toolset_support_component
' Research artifact (project-researcher) — toolset-support verification, not an HLD.
' Maps each node's §1 responsibilities to the §3(d) language/toolset picks;
' requirement numbers from requirements/m1-cooperative-awareness.md (R1-R25).
title Per-node toolset support — §1 responsibilities on the §3 stack picks (verification view)

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam wrapWidth 230
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center

node "Bench node — Scenario Player\n<b>Python</b> + C++ encode component\n(team-built container)" as bench {
  [Scenario engine\nR10 trajectories, config-driven] as B_ENG
  [CPM emission at varying rates\nR11 — Vanetza ITS2 encode (C++) / JSON P1] as B_EMIT
  [Impairment engine\nR12 — pre-emission drop/delay/jitter] as B_IMP
  [LOS-filtered ego sensor view\nR13 — geometry from ground truth] as B_LOS
  [Ego GNSS feed\nR9 source — telux-shaped JSON fixes] as B_GNSS
  [God view + jury dashboard\nR14 — SSE/polling, no WebSocket] as B_DASH
  [Optional modem config responses\n§1 optional — scripted acks] as B_CFG
}

node "V2X ECU\n<b>C++17</b> (skill-gated F6)\n(app-level Linux container)" as v2x {
  [Adapter seam IV2xRadio-mirror\nR5 — POSIX/Asio UDP below seam] as V_ADP
  [Modem stub FSM + fail-inject\nR6 — simulated config call flow] as V_STUB
  [Rx pipeline decode-validate-dedupe\nR7 — Vanetza ITS2 CPM decode] as V_RX
  [Ego Tx CPM construct + broadcast\nR8 — same Vanetza codec, encode side] as V_TX
  [GNSS forward subscribeLocation\nR9 — JSON fixes to ADA] as V_GNSS
}

node "ADA ECU\n<b>Python 3.11+</b>\n(app-level Linux container)" as ada {
  [Track store + admission\nR15 — 10 Hz x 3 objects] as A_STORE
  [CRA plugin abstraction\nR16 — extensible warning scenarios] as A_CRA
  [NLOS/TTC realization\nR17 — d_AC composition + risk states] as A_RISK
  [Evidence logging\nR23 — JSONL event list] as A_LOG
  [Camera detection bonus\nR21 — YOLO11n ONNX CPU, timeboxed] as A_DET
}

node "IVI ECU — provided AAOS full vECU\n<b>Kotlin</b> + Jetpack Compose" as ivi {
  [UDP foreground service\nR4 consumer — DatagramSocket, UI-free module] as I_UDP
  [HMI shell + app switching\nR18 — Compose, heads-up CATEGORY_NAVIGATION] as I_SHELL
  [Warning-view intent entry (exported)\nR18/F15 foundation — future wake-on-warning door] as I_ENTRY
  [3D god view\nR19 — SceneView/Filament, gated (GPU risk)] as I_3D
  [2D floor + 2D-3D toggle\nR19 — Compose Canvas, in-seam fallback] as I_2D
}

B_ENG --> B_EMIT
B_EMIT --> B_IMP
B_IMP --> V_ADP : R1/R2 CPM wire (UDP, Ethernet pin)\nemulates the modem connection point
B_GNSS --> V_ADP : R9 GNSS fixes (UDP JSON)
B_CFG ..> V_STUB : optional control channel\n(committed config answer = in-node R6 stub)
B_LOS --> A_STORE : R3 objects, source=own_sensor
V_ADP --> V_RX
V_RX --> A_STORE : R3 relayed object + B pose (JSON)
A_STORE --> V_TX : R8 store snapshot
V_GNSS --> A_RISK : R9 ego fixes
A_STORE --> A_CRA
A_CRA --> A_RISK
A_RISK --> I_UDP : R4 warning events + 10 Hz state (UDP JSON)
A_RISK --> B_DASH : R14 risk push
I_UDP --> I_SHELL
I_SHELL --> I_ENTRY : M1 idle-to-warning transition\n(same door a future orchestrator uses)
I_ENTRY --> I_3D
I_ENTRY --> I_2D

@enduml
